tication reference content (Bearer Token, API Key, scopes, error references)\n- ✅ `mkdocs.yml` — The `Authentication: api/authentication.md` entry is added to the `nav` under `API`, between Overview and Errors (logical placement)\n- ✅ Validation will continue to pass — `scripts/validate_repo.py` only checks that `site_name:` and `nav:` exist in `mkdocs.yml` and that certain required files exist. None of those are affected.\n\n### Limitation\n\nI was unable to commit the changes due to a **403 permission error** on the repository — the PAT token lacks write access. The changes above are ready to be applied by a user with appropriate permissions.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 587, "prompt_tokens": 9531, "total_tokens": 10118, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 44, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9088, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0007361118, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002254218, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00051069}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780865611-4dH9BcnNpCrW5SuglE8L", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3dc-b771-7f83-8b29-c64acec2a3cb-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9531, "output_tokens": 587, "total_tokens": 10118, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9088}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 44}}}}]}}}
